India's Biggest GenAI Summit for developers

Partner with us

MLDS brings together India’s leading innovators and developers from across technologies and other cutting-edge fields to share their insights and experiences. Attendees will explore the latest tools, advancements, and breakthrough technologies, gaining exclusive insights into emerging trends and developer products shaping the future of software development.

MLDS 2025

Contact Us Directly For More Information Or Leave A Message And We’ll Get Back To You ASAP

E: info@aimmediahouse.com

When & Where

Thursday to Friday
February 6 – 7, 2025

NIMHANS Convention Center, Bengaluru, India

What to expect

3 Tracks over 3 days –

  • Keynotes/ Tech talks (Hall 1)
  • Tech Talks/ workshops (Hall 2)
  • Paper Presentation (Hall 3)

Besides – Mentoring sessions, Hackathon, Awards, Exhibition, Live Coding, Competitions & a lot more

Our Past Sponsors

To know more details, write to info@aimmediahouse.com

Partner with us

Grab your ticket for a unique experience of inspiration, meeting and networking with top developers in India

Book your tickets at the earliest. We have a hard stop at 1000 passes.

Note: Ticket Pricing to change at any time.

  • 1 Day Pass

  • Access to all in-person tracks & workshops
  • Access the recorded sessions later
  • Access to in-person networking with attendees & speakers
  • Conference Lunch for 1 Day
  • No Group Discount Available
  • ₹7000
Recommended

  • Full Access Passes

    All Access 3 Day Pass
  • Access to all in-person tracks & workshops
  • Access the recorded sessions later
  • Access to in-person networking with attendees & speakers
  • Conference Lunch for all 3 days
  • No Group Discount Available
  • ₹15000

India's Biggest GenAI Summit for developers

It was a great privilege to attend the Machine Learning Developers Summit 2023 organized by Analytics India Magazine. A place where the great ML minds of India come together to share their knowledge. This summit provided me a great exposure and experience. I had the chance to meet a lot of people, learn a lot of things, and was fascinated by the ambiance and knowledge of the attendees.

Nawin Raj Kumar (NRK) S

Nunnari Labs

It was a great experience to be a part of the Machine Learning Developers Summit (MLDS) 2023 on 19 & 20 January 2023. MLDS 2023 has been a superb platform for machine learning enthusiasts focusing on the innovations and trends happening in the Machine learning space, enabling them to understand and connect with top ML innovators from leading tech firms. The Summit has helped immensely in engaging with industry leaders and discussing the deployment of the latest ML framework and solutions for business use cases.

Unmeesh Sankpal

Opira Group

Machine Learning Developers Summit 2023 was truly magical! The best of the best in the industry came together to discuss, plan and strategise about the future of the AI industry in India. Kudos to Analytics India Magazine team for pulling this marvel off.

Abhijeet Katte

Lonere Labs

Team Michelin had a great time attending as well as speaking at the Machine Learning Developers Summit 2023. 2 days of experience sharing with some of the industry’s leading AI and ML practitioners from different organisations coming together to offer valuable insights on the state of the industry today.

Priya Kulashri

Michelin

Our upcoming events

“Generative models allow machines to learn from data and then create new, original content, and they have the potential to revolutionize industries from music to fashion to gaming.”

~Yann LeCun, Director of AI Research at Facebook
